description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Entry of the Crusaders in Constantinople / Eugène Delacroix
-Women of Algiers / Eugène Delacroix
-The Voyage of Life: Youth / Thomas Cole
-Charles IV of Spain and His Family / Francisco Goya
-The Execution of Lady Jane Grey / Paul Delaroche
-The Barque of Dante / Eugène Delacroix
-Combat Between the Giaour and the Pasha/ Eugène Delacroix
-The Course of Empire: The Consummation of Empire / Thomas Cole
-The 1821 Derby at Epsom / Théodore Géricault
-The Raft of the Medusa / Théodore Géricault
name: Masterpieces of World  - Romanticism -
